name: Satheesh Madhavan
description:
Influences -
Indian, Jamaican and a lot of cross culture vibe..

Sattessh Madhavan is the foundation Dj/Selector from Hyderabad roots, his musical expression is influenced by various eclectic styles of music that helps the soul to move forward spiritually, connecting nature and cosmos on the whole which involves the dissolving of the ego and identify the true “self”

Stage Name: Mr Nobody

Spreading the vibe of conscious Reggae, Dancehall and various soulful musical styles to the community.

name: Balasubramaniam
description:
Dakta Dub is India's very own international artist, started djing in Budapest, Hungary with www.tilos.hu, one of the biggest underground radio station in Europe. His is a eclectic Sounding artists in terms of Tone and Timbre.
Rooted in Indian and dub music influences, dakta is a True Rasta in Belief.
His sets travel through a dimensions from down tempo to groovier floor hitting tunes from various genres of music.
